						<p class="txt-shadow-lite">
							We’ll meet with you to understand your church’s needs and current
							systems to develop and implement a system tailored to your needs.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="step">
					<div class="number-container">
						<!--?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?-->
						<svg
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
							><path
								fill-rule="evenodd"
								clip-rule="evenodd"
								d="M3.6 2.25C2.85442 2.25 2.25 2.85441 2.25 3.6V20.4C2.25 21.1456 2.85441 21.75 3.6 21.75H20.4C21.1456 21.75 21.75 21.1456 21.75 20.4V3.6C21.75 2.85442 21.1456 2.25 20.4 2.25H3.6ZM10.25 10.4C10.25 9.46073 10.9749 8.75 11.8077 8.75C12.6405 8.75 13.3654 9.46073 13.3654 10.4C13.3654 10.7213 13.2793 11.0178 13.1324 11.2683C12.67 12.057 11.6782 13.0782 10.7378 13.9441C10.2789 14.3665 9.85144 14.7348 9.53856 14.9976C9.3823 15.1289 9.2551 15.2334 9.16743 15.3047C9.12361 15.3404 9.0897 15.3677 9.06701 15.3859L9.04159 15.4063L9.0355 15.4111L9.03417 15.4122L9.034 15.4123L9.03394 15.4124C8.78395 15.6107 8.68678 15.9454 8.79175 16.2467C8.89672 16.5481 9.18089 16.75 9.5 16.75H14.5C14.9142 16.75 15.25 16.4142 15.25 16C15.25 15.5858 14.9142 15.25 14.5 15.25H11.5319C11.6048 15.1841 11.6789 15.1165 11.7537 15.0476C12.6904 14.1853 13.8383 13.0302 14.4265 12.027C14.7059 11.5504 14.8654 10.9926 14.8654 10.4C14.8654 8.6883 13.5239 7.25 11.8077 7.25C10.0915 7.25 8.75 8.6883 8.75 10.4V10.8C8.75 11.2142 9.08579 11.55 9.5 11.55C9.91421 11.55 10.25 11.2142 10.25 10.8V10.4Z"
							></path></svg
						>
					</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3 class="hd-shadow-lite">Use Your New Playbooks</h3>
						<p class="txt-shadow-lite">
							Your playbooks will be designed specifically for your church using
							custom automations, workflows, templates and proven processes.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="step">
					<div class="number-container">
						<!--?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?-->
						<svg
							viewBox="0 0 24 24"
							fill="none"
							xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
							><path
								fill-rule="evenodd"
								clip-rule="evenodd"
								d="M2.25 3.6C2.25 2.85441 2.85442 2.25 3.6 2.25H20.4C21.1456 2.25 21.75 2.85442 21.75 3.6V20.4C21.75 21.1456 21.1456 21.75 20.4 21.75H3.6C2.85441 21.75 2.25 21.1456 2.25 20.4V3.6ZM12 8.75C13.1313 8.75 13.75 9.45717 13.75 10C13.75 10.4191 13.6329 10.7217 13.4616 10.9111C13.3018 11.0877 13.0195 11.25 12.5 11.25C12.0858 11.25 11.75 11.5858 11.75 12C11.75 12.4142 12.0858 12.75 12.5 12.75C13.0195 12.75 13.3018 12.9123 13.4616 13.0889C13.6329 13.2783 13.75 13.5809 13.75 14C13.75 14.5428 13.1313 15.25 12 15.25C10.8687 15.25 10.25 14.5428 10.25 14C10.25 13.5858 9.91421 13.25 9.5 13.25C9.08579 13.25 8.75 13.5858 8.75 14C8.75 15.6663 10.3699 16.75 12 16.75C13.6301 16.75 15.25 15.6663 15.25 14C15.25 13.3145 15.0575 12.6171 14.574 12.0826C14.5484 12.0544 14.5223 12.0269 14.4955 12C14.5223 11.9732 14.5484 11.9456 14.574 11.9174C15.0575 11.3829 15.25 10.6855 15.25 10C15.25 8.33369 13.6301 7.25 12 7.25C10.3699 7.25 8.75 8.33369 8.75 10C8.75 10.4142 9.08579 10.75 9.5 10.75C9.91421 10.75 10.25 10.4142 10.25 10C10.25 9.45717 10.8687 8.75 12 8.75Z"
